<a href="apigee.com/docs/enterprise/enterprise_home">Home</a> > <a href="/api-resources">Platform API Reference</a> > <a href="/api_resources/17-developer-apps">Developer Apps</a> > Gets the count of API resources  defined in API products approved for a developer app in an organization</div>

<h1>Gets the count of API resources  defined in API products approved for a developer app in an organization</h1> 
</p>

<div class="row">
	<div class="span6"><p>
		<b>API Platform Base Path:</b>
		<h3><p>https://api.enterprise.apigee.com/v1/o/{org_name}</p></h3>
		<b>API Resource Path:</b>
		<p>/developers/{developer_email}/apps/{app_name}?&amp;quot;query=count&amp;entity={entity_name}&amp;quot;</p>
		<p>
		Gets a count of all API Resources (URIs) in the API Products accessible by an App
		</p>
	</div>

	<div class="span6">
		<p>
		<b>Verb:</b>
		<span class="verb-GET">GET</span>
		</p>
		<b>Auth:</b>
		Basic Auth
		</p>



	</div>
</div>



<div class="span24"><p>
Returns a count of all API Resources (URIs) available to be access by an app through the API products the app is associated with.
</p>



<b>cURL:</b>
<pre>curl -u myname:mypass https://api.enterprise.apigee.com/v1/o/{myorg}/{developerEmail}/apps/{appname}?query=count&amp;entity=apiresources</pre>



<b>Sample Response:</b> 
	<pre>{
  &quot;value&quot; : 3
}</pre>




</div>










            </div>
        </div><!--/row-->
